  "text": "MINISTRY OF ENVIRONMENT AND FORESTS NOTIFICATION New Delhi, the 22nd September 2003 S.O. 1091 (E) In exercise of the powers conferred by Sub-section (2) of Section 1 of the Wild Life (Protection) Act, 2002 (16 of 2003), the Central Government hereby appoints the 22nd day of September, 2003 as the date on which section 6 of the said Act shall come into force. [F.No 6-1/2003 WL-I] VINOD RISHI, Addl. Director, General of Forests -- 1 of 1 --",
